overview:
QuickMedical is a national distributor of medical equipment and medical supplies. Founded in 1993, QuickMedical now carries over 26,000 medical products, healthcare equipment, and professional medical supplies. Look for diagnostic equipment, exam tables, weighing and measuring devices, and medical basics such as stethoscopes, thermometers, and sphygmomanometers. QuickMedical also offers a wide selection of professional medical supplies; everything from patient care, to blood testing, to exam room products. Find quality and affordable disposables and medical supplies for the clinic, hospital, or home care environment.

Recently QuickMedical has introduced a diabetes supply program, now accepting Medicare for diabetes supplies. Call QuickMedical and speak with a friendly staff member for any assistance 1-888-345-4858. Check out our unique and search friendly website for medical product information, medical supply videos, and QuickMedical’s Medical Equipment and Supply Blog.
